  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1462961">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1462961/" class="title-link">很有启发性的书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1462961"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/kerria/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/kerria/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">[已注销]</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-08-05"
      class="main-meta">2008-08-05 21:40:46</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1462961_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    主体内容还可以，但并无特别新奇之处。可是每章之后的“请思考……”却很有趣；可以先看这部分，再看前面的内容。这是一本看的时候没什么感觉，合上却让人回味让人怀念的书。   值得一读。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1462961_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1462961_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评15篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
