        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/januery/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2176515-15.jpg" alt="Σελήνη" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/30387301/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/30387301/" class="">第100页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/januery/" class=" " title="Σελήνη">Σελήνη</a>
                (我只负责精彩  一切自有安排)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="30387301">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">人非其所是，是其所非。 --黑格尔</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-02-03 11:05</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                人非其所是，是其所非。 --黑格尔
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
